{
  "stem": "6526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I ran back to a house where I knew that there is a basement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I ran into the basement, stayed there the whole day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And about 3:00, 4:00 in the morning, I walked out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I walked to Minsk Mazowiecki, 16 kilometers, 10 miles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I knew that there are still Jews working on the railroad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was there for about 10 days until I found a man from the Polish underground that used to help out Jews get new identities, Polish passports.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that time, another man from my town, we met together and said, lets get an apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Also was getting two passports and that meant we'll get us the place, and we'll go to Warsaw to stay there, what happened.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was in December, more or less about December 15-- December 15 in 1942.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were living in an apartment of a woman that her husband was a military-- an officer, Polish officer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Whether this officer was dead already or was captured, we don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They weren't sure whether he was alive or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we also got news that the Jews in Warsaw ghetto are still there and they going outside to do clean up the broken up buildings, the broken up houses.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this is where they work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they used to get-- take out some merchandise to sell to Poles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And sort of-- and we met [POLISH] from our town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we met him and he said, it's OK to come in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they'll know a day or two before, and being that we'll have a place outside, we'll just go out to work and we'll never come back to work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We'll stay in the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was our intention.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
